          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Every woman dreams of a destination wedding, but the planning for the wedding needs to be different as well! Whether your vows are echoed on a sunlit beach, a royal court, a vineyard or under the stars, your wedding jewelry should move as gracefully as you do. The right destination wedding jewelry does not just sparkle, but carries the story of your forever with deeper meaning, matches the theme of your wedding and is comfortable. Here’s your complete guide to selecting, styling, and safeguarding your destination wedding accessories. </p>",
