            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1_2305159d-13b4-4afc-8ff6-d5eff2476aba.jpg",
            "text": "<p>A destination wedding means movement, changing climates, and multiple looks and wedding jewelry for bride needs to adapt to all three. These pieces need to embody elegance while being travel friendly, lightweight, and versatile. Choose bridal jewelry with tight clasps, secure prongs, and with minimal maintenance needs. We believe that every piece should be crafted keeping these in mind. Our jewelry pieces are timeless companions that are versatile for every look and embody a bride’s dream day! </p>",
